<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        td {
            padding: 10px;
            border: none;
        }
        .button {
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            border: none;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .mailHeader{
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .mailBody{
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .orderId{
            text-align: left;
            padding: 10px 0;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #999999;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .subheader {
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999999;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            td {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <table class="mailHeader">
        <tr>
            <td class="header">
                {{app_name}}
            </td>
            <td class="orderId">
                Order {{orderId}}
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="subheader">
                Thank you for your purchase!
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <table class="mailBody">
        
        <tr>
            <td>
                Hi {{name}},<br>
                your package is under preparation. We will do our best to deliver the products as early as we can. Appreciate your patience and understanding. 
                <br><br>
                Please note that there could be local tariffs charged on the package. In such a case, the local customs will contact you directly to process the tariff settlement. But this case doesn't always happen.

            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align:center">
                <a href="{{resetpassURL}}" class="button">View your order</a>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>                
                If you have any questions, please go to our <a href="{{websiteURL}}">official website</a> and submit a request for further help.
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <div class="footer">
                    <p>&copy; 2024 {{app_name}}. All rights reserved.</p>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>